content:
A Test Procedure tests a calculation performed by another Integration Procedure. Enable the Tracking Service for Integration Procedures. Create the Integration Procedure to be tested. See Create a Conditional Block Example with If-Elseif-Else Logic. Mock a Response in the Tested Integration Procedure. 

Create an Example Test Procedure. After you mock a response, create the Test Procedure that tests a calculation it performs. Run the Test Procedure from IDX Workbench.
title: Test Procedures for OmniStudio Integration
